## File Structure

### Core Files

#### Main Application Files
- **`src/main.jsx`**: Application entry point
- **`src/App.jsx`**: Main application component with routing
- **`src/App.css`**: Global application styles
- **`index.html`**: HTML template

#### Component Organization
- **`src/components/`**: Reusable components organized by functionality
- **`src/pages/`**: Page-level components for different routes
- **`src/hooks/`**: Custom React hooks for state management
- **`src/data/`**: Static data files (bookings, hubs)

#### Styling System
- **CSS Modules**: Each component has its own `.module.css` file
- **Global Styles**: `src/styles/` contains global variables and styles
- **Responsive Breakpoints**: Consistent breakpoints across all components

